WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:03.043
Previously on Bates Motel...

00:03.111 --> 00:04.945
Do you remember anything?

00:05.013 --> 00:07.481
I've never seen anyone
go into a hole like that.

00:07.549 --> 00:09.766
I mean, you were, like, not there.

00:09.797 --> 00:12.052
Your mom warned me not to
talk about your blackouts.

00:12.120 --> 00:14.121
You told her something
happens to me when I black out.

00:14.189 --> 00:16.155
You said I change, that I'm not myself.

00:16.258 --> 00:18.993
Who am I, mother? Who
am I and what do I do?

00:19.094 --> 00:20.194
Here I am. Talk.

00:20.295 --> 00:21.328
Zane Morgan.

00:21.396 --> 00:22.463
What about him?

00:22.564 --> 00:23.697
You can take him out.

00:23.765 --> 00:25.566
Dylan, Nick Ford has Norman.

00:25.667 --> 00:28.269
He kidnapped him. He
won't tell me where he is.

00:28.370 --> 00:31.038
You need to convince Dylan
to do what I want him to do.

00:31.139 --> 00:34.441
If you tell your friend
Sheriff Romero or anyone else,

00:34.509 --> 00:36.043
Norman will be dead.

00:37.579 --> 00:38.612
I couldn't get to him.

00:38.680 --> 00:40.581
I'm really sorry to hear that.

